title: 2MNY Productions Video Projects
description:
Video Projects directed by Michael Zakes, 2MNY Bananas Productions.


Another Dimension: Grant Specht takes a short odyssey through another dimension where nothing is what it seems. A strange experiment in film special effects.

The Big Squeeze: In consideration for the Brown University 2008 Ivy Film Festival. When nature calls; a relaxing time on the john goes horribly wrong. For immature audiences only. Starring Grant Specht in a 3 minute short.

Game 1 & 2: Two minute long shorts edited using the same footage and different audio tracks for different results.

Quesadillas: My directorial debut. A short, relaxing, silent film about making dinner.
